    "# 87. The Hub-and-Spoke Network Design Problem\n",
    "\n",
    "## Tier 7: The Human-AI Symbiotic Partnership\n",
    "\n",
    "### Key assumptions\n",
    "- Human expertise and AI capabilities can be synergistically combined\n",
    "- Trust between human and AI partners develops through successful collaboration\n",
    "- Humans provide strategic guidance, AI provides computational optimization\n",
    "- Explainable AI enables humans to understand and trust AI recommendations\n",
    "- Learning systems improve both human and AI performance over time\n",
    "\n",
    "### Approach (step-by-step)\n",
    "1. **Partnership Initialization**: Define human expertise areas and AI capabilities\n",
    "2. **Strategic Input**: Humans provide high-level strategic objectives and constraints\n",
    "3. **AI Optimization**: AI generates optimal solutions considering human input\n",
    "4. **Explainable Analysis**: AI provides explanations for its recommendations\n",
    "5. **Human Evaluation**: Humans evaluate and refine AI recommendations\n",
    "6. **Trust Development**: Update trust metrics based on collaboration success\n",
    "7. **Learning Integration**: Both human and AI learn from the collaborative process\n",
    "\n",
    "### What to look for in the results\n",
    "- Improved solution quality through human-AI collaboration\n",
    "- Trust development metrics over time\n",
    "- Explainable AI recommendations with clear reasoning\n",
    "- Learning curves showing performance improvement\n",
    "- Balanced human oversight with AI optimization\n",
    "\n",
    "### Concrete example (from the source)\n",
    "We'll implement the 12-node Global Logistics Alliance example where human-AI partnership achieves 18% better solutions than AI alone, with trust scores improving from 0.6 to 0.92 over 10 collaborative iterations."
   ]
