    "### Why this Tier exists vs earlier Tiers\n",
    "Tier 7 introduces human-AI symbiotic partnership to overcome limitations of purely automated optimization:\n",
    "- **Human expertise integration**: Leverages domain knowledge that AI cannot capture from data alone\n",
    "- **Trust-based collaboration**: Builds trust between human decision-makers and AI systems\n",
    "- **Explainable AI**: Provides transparent reasoning for AI recommendations\n",
    "- **Adaptive learning**: Both human and AI learn and improve through collaboration\n",
    "- **Strategic alignment**: Ensures AI solutions align with human strategic objectives\n",
    "\n",
    "### Pros / Cons vs earlier Tiers\n",
    "**Pros vs Tier 1-6 (Automated Methods):**\n",
    "- **Strategic wisdom**: Incorporates human strategic thinking and experience\n",
    "- **Contextual understanding**: Humans provide context that AI may miss\n",
    "- **Trust building**: Develops trust in AI systems through transparent collaboration\n",
    "- **Adaptive improvement**: Learning system improves both human and AI performance\n",
    "- **Risk mitigation**: Human oversight reduces risk of AI errors or unintended consequences\n",
    "\n",
    "**Pros vs Tier 5 (Digital Twin):**\n",
    "- **Human intuition**: Combines data-driven insights with human intuition\n",
    "- **Strategic flexibility**: Humans can adapt strategy based on changing business conditions\n",
    "- **Explainability**: Human-AI dialogue provides better understanding than automated systems\n",
    "- **Trust development**: Active collaboration builds deeper trust than passive monitoring\n",
    "- **Creativity**: Human creativity combined with AI computational power\n",
    "\n",
    "**Cons:**\n",
    "- **Human dependency**: Requires human time and expertise\n",
    "- **Subjectivity**: Human preferences may introduce bias\n",
